title: Frank Lloyd Wright Coonley Trivet—Playhouse
description:
Inspired by the art glass window triptych found in the Avery Coonley Playhouse, designed by Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867–1959), this absorbent stone trivet is a colorful addition to any tabletop. Produced by a heat transfer process, with cork backing. Made in the USA. 

7 in sq.
